{"tid":1947011,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【立法會選舉反擊戰】飲食界真係告急！五分鐘超簡單超快登記法！","createTime":"2020-03-28T04:01:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-03T10:04:53.000Z","uid":127929,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"c2fb7fc8ab77c5937d6705a0ee18b633421f317d","tid":1947011,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T04:01:52.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">飲食界</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">告急情況：</span><br />\n1. 登記率極低：根據2019既資料，現時食環署發出的食物業牌照超過2萬個，但飲食界已登記選民合共僅4,408個，即<span style=\"color: red;\">登記率只有2成！</span><br />\n2. 藍票比例極高：而以2016年立法會選舉為例，張宇人以2,438票擊敗民主派候選人伍永德的647票 (即係以目前既4千幾飲食界選票中，超過7成係鐵票)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">登記資格：</span>只要持有食環署食物業牌照，就可以登記成為飲食界選民(注意：飲食界分為團體票及個人票，店主要留意自己是否為個人持牌，即個人票)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">截止日期：</span>2/4/2020 (下星期四)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">如何遞交申請：</span><br />\n1. 個人票：<br />\n如果你本身<span style=\"color: red;\">有</span>傳統功能界別 或 你<span style=\"color: red;\">有</span>超級區議會界別既投票資格，<span style=\"color: red;\">你必須填寫 REO-43</span>( <a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-43(C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Fform%2FREO-43%28C&d=g1YLBr7c5t2fgTVFseaOq0BBI%2BG%2BtQAW9Loz3QxUp%2BM%3D&h=feea8087\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-43(C</a>).pdf )，以更改功能界別選民。如果你<span style=\"color: red;\">不是</span>任何傳統功能界別 或 你<span style=\"color: red;\">不是</span>超級區議會界別既選民，請填寫表格 REO-41( <a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-41(C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Fform%2FREO-41%28C&d=g1YLBr7c5t2fgTVFseaOq0BBI%2BG%2BtQAW9Loz3QxUp%2BM%3D&h=b1e661e0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-41(C</a>).pdf )<br />\n<br />\n2. 團體票<br />\n請填寫表格 REO-42 ( <a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-42(C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Fform%2FREO-42%28C&d=g1YLBr7c5t2fgTVFseaOq0BBI%2BG%2BtQAW9Loz3QxUp%2BM%3D&h=34d47314\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-42(C</a>).pdf )<br />\n<br />\n請把已填妥及由你或你的團體的負責人和獲授權代表簽署（如屬團體申請）的申請表格，<span style=\"color: gold;\">在4月2日(下星期四)前</span>，以<span style=\"color: red;\">郵遞方式</span>寄回<strong>九龍九龍灣展貿徑一號九龍灣國際展貿中心十三樓</strong>或傳真至 2891 1180。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">source:</span> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/gn/cat_c.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Fgn%2Fcat_c.pdf&d=g1YLBr7c5t2fgTVFseaOq0BBI%2BG%2BtQAW9Loz3QxUp%2BM%3D&h=6987545d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/gn/cat_c.pdf</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200328/XPSAFOUIDH4P7UKLRYUO7LJP5E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200328%2FXPSAFOUIDH4P7UKLRYUO7LJP5E%2F&d=g1YLBr7c5t2fgTVFseaOq0BBI%2BG%2BtQAW9Loz3QxUp%2BM%3D&h=4fc85949\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200328%2FXPSAFOUIDH4P7UKLRYUO7LJP5E%2F&h=2731c843\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200328/XPSAFOUIDH4P7UKLRYUO7LJP5E/</a><br />\n記者 李雨夢<br />\n美心擁276間持牌食肆 造就大量鐵票<br />\n「民間飲食界選民登記小隊」翻查食環署的食肆牌照發現，美心集團旗下有276間持牌食肆、大家樂有161間、稻香約46間、富臨約60間、太興約118間。若以上5個「深藍」大集團透過不同公司，為旗下持牌食肆登記作飲食界選民，粗略估計或有超過600鐵票支持張宇人。2016年立法會選舉，張宇人以2,438票擊敗民主派候選人伍永德的647票。"},{"pid":"153af0223c60c5e93bdfc3d992a5cbcd1daca271","tid":1947011,"uid":127929,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T04:03:55.000Z","msg":"寫漏左五分鐘係點計出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />連登仔速度<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：先用2分鐘填係pdf度直接填表，再用1分鐘print出黎，然後用1分鐘入好信封，最後個1分鐘鳩衝去郵政局寄信<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de8c469597d53e43d632caa97024ee1b74ac3616","tid":1947011,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T04:04:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f40c9abfb2c4cf831c0d95e1fc587dad4c177e5","tid":1947011,"uid":127929,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T04:10:09.000Z","msg":"推到比杜文澤YellopenRice團隊知，今次係繼推廣攝衫之後再一次想佢幫幫手單聲黃店鼓勵下大家登記<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n揀飲擇食，只食<span style=\"color: gold;\">黃店</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MNVemSC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMNVemSC.jpg&h=de875c82&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8d6db26318f685afe1e96d424206e9ba349cb7fb","tid":1947011,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T04:10:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2046ea6c55d1c6301146edb4eb3a06e7fcc56087","tid":1947011,"uid":146285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T04:10:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"64aaa0b7befa11442da2afcb39e011a907eb7d15","tid":1947011,"uid":146285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T04:11:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ae25af944b9960cd2f1339f1a3345a9374227b83","tid":1947011,"uid":19640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T04:11:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc29010f82d3954f7a883a3595763ec9cb71bc33","tid":1947011,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T04:12:32.000Z","msg":"推, 寫左成粒鐘架, 大家比下面唔係選民都推一推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d87f3bc249714e466ef43758da940aa7985c83e9","tid":1947011,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T04:13:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f8bf524f8c795c73eede9b5623c6d59d7026d87e","tid":1947011,"uid":3457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T04:13:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"60ccc8f34352114e89b16d7a5a1177e443892bd3","tid":1947011,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T04:13:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cf17602fd945dc739d1b4ce0a119a04c020466c6","tid":1947011,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T04:13:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8609a7fec9023b9df3457bd4600d244f325a9956","tid":1947011,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T04:13:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"625cb66333512c320dc4ea68ec5d5a9195e869bb","tid":1947011,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T04:13:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0ea3b8fbaa5a37441a236f42ed9d6bbd64dfee68","tid":1947011,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T04:13:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"48341e264355a8f6845c61fe9eb12126202492c9","tid":1947011,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T04:14:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8630361090eb94cae1b339f38edf30c050ee3568","tid":1947011,"uid":189132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T04:14:57.00